A motorist was shot dead on the N2 on Saturday and a female driver was shot and killed in Nyanga on Thursday. Police spokesperson Andre Traut said: “On Saturday, at about 10.30pm, a man was shot and killed in his Toyota Fortuner on the N2 in Khayelitsha,” Traut said. The female driver killed in Nyanga was shot just metres away from a police station. “On Thursday, at about 10.30pm, a 31-year-old woman was shot in Ntlangano Crescent, Nyanga. The victim was inside her Toyota Aygo at the time of the attack,” the police spokesperson said. Any member of the public with information or clues can anonymously contact Crime Stop on 08600 10111 or alternatively SMS Crime Line on 32211. Cape Times